All MoBs at lvl 50+ have the ability to summon.  But don't worry too much about how hard this makes them to solo, it'll be a looong time before you are able to solo them anyway ;)<br>
<br>
No, it doesn't make them impossible to fight without a tank.  Just don't aggro them or you'll get summoned.  Two magicians can take down a lvl 50, one magician and a cleric can, one magician and a necro can, etc etc.    All it really does is require you to pay a little more attention to not aggroing the MoB.  <br>
<br>
And, just because they *can* summon, that doesn't mean that they *will* summon.  If you are close by the MoB may very well just run over and whack you as oppose to summoning you.  In fact, our party was jumped by Lodzil once before we were fully ready and I ran it in a circle around the island with only being summoned once.   <br>
<br>
The biggest problem you will find is mobs that can gate *and* summon.  Those are really, really nasty.   Nothing breaks up a plane run like the PoG gating (or really warping as we've seen) and then summoning your raiding party one by one to it to beat on.   <p> <br>
<b>Ez</b> <br>
